@startuml
title Diagramme de séquence — Impression & Scan QR Code (ECB)

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam roundcorner 5
skinparam LifeLineBorderColor #333333
skinparam SequenceGroupBorderColor #888888
skinparam SequenceGroupFontColor #333333
skinparam SequenceGroupBackgroundColor #F5F5F5

' ECB Stereotypes
actor "Collaborateur" as U
actor "Client (Public)" as CL
boundary "Interface (App)" as I <<Boundary>>
boundary "Page Publique (Web)" as P <<Boundary>>
control "FactureComponent" as FC <<Control>>
control "PublicController" as PC <<Control>>
entity "Facture" as F <<Entity>>

== Impression & Téléchargement (Interacteurs Authentifiés) ==

U -> I : cliquer sur "Imprimer"
activate U
activate I
I -> FC : imprimer()
activate FC
FC --> I : window.print()
deactivate FC
I --> U : Document PDF / Impression
deactivate I
deactivate U

== Scan du QR Code (Impression et Scan) ==

note over U, CL : Le scan s'effectue sur le document\n(Aucune authentification requise)

group Accès via QR Code
    U -> P : Scanner le QR Code
    activate U
    activate P
    CL -> P : Scanner le QR Code
    activate CL
    
    P -> PC : GET /api/public/factures/{id}
    activate PC
    PC -> F : Récupérer statut en temps réel
    activate F
    F --> PC : Données de la facture
    deactivate F
    PC --> P : Affichage des informations
    deactivate PC
    
    P --> CL : Statut vérifié
    deactivate CL
    P --> U : Statut vérifié
    deactivate P
    deactivate U
end

@enduml
